title: Kids "GET STRONG" 💪 Full Body Strength Training Workout!🔥
description:
This week's kids workout is to GET STRONG! We are doing the best KIDS STRENGTH TRAINING EXERCISES to help you get stronger, go faster and play your best!

We put out new kids workouts every week - subscribe to our channels: @GVOKids 

Go check out Greyson's new channel also @GreysonPumple 

Disclaimer: This is general fitness only. Please check with your doctor or health care provider to see if this video is safe for you and your kids. You are responsible for you and your child's own safety. Don’t do anything that feels unsafe for you or your child. Stop if you have any pain or discomfort, bleeding, chest pain or shortness of breath, dizziness or if you feel unwell. Jessica Pumple is a registered dietitian, kids fitness instructor and ballet teacher making fitness fun for kids!

channelDescription:
GVO Kids is the ultimate YouTube channel for kids who love fun, fitness, creativity, and laughter! Join siblings Vivien (11), Greyson (12), and Octavia (6) on their exciting adventures filled with engaging workout challenges, relatable skits, dance, and imaginative play. From solving hilarious mishaps like "spilled slime" to epic “Scavenger hunt” games, GVO Kids is all about good vibes, big laughs, and making every day extraordinary. Perfect for kids who want to feel part of a fun-loving family and enjoy entertaining, age-appropriate content that sparks joy and creativity!
Check out Greyson's channel! @greysonpumple
